<td>/[service]-[city]</td>
<td>/drain-cleaning-dallas</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Location Page</td>
<td>/areas/[city]</td>
<td>/areas/frisco-tx</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Blog Post</td>
<td>/blog/[topic]</td>
<td>/blog/how-to-unclog-drain</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Keep URLs short. Avoid stop words. Include the primary keyword. Use hyphens, not underscores.</p>
